io.druid.query

Class Druids.SelectQueryBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.druid.query.Druids.SelectQueryBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    Druids

    public static class Druids.SelectQueryBuilder
extends Object
    A Builder for SelectQuery. Required: dataSource(), intervals() must be called before build() Usage example: 
    
   SelectQuery query = new SelectQueryBuilder()
                                  .dataSource("Example")
                                  .interval("2010/2013")
                                  .build();
    See Also:
    SelectQuery
